tracing_representation_progression.pdf\nTotal pages: 27\nPages per chunk: 3\nCreated 9 chunk files in: papers/pages\nManifest: papers/pages/2406.14479_tracing_representation_progression_manifest.txt\nSplitting PDF: papers/2411.08197_decodable_information.pdf\nTotal pages: 21\nPages per chunk: 3\nObject 209 0 not defined.\nObject 372 0 not defined.\nCreated 7 chunk files in: papers/pages\nManifest: papers/pages/2411.08197_decodable_information_manifest.txt\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
